message.body: Hey ####! We're going to be grilling out some kabobs Friday night if you guys want to come by!
Yes!! That sounds great and we're actually free!
Wonderful! I think we'll start grilling around 630 ish. Are you guys veg?
Great! ###### is. Let us know if there's anything veg-friendly we can bring. And we'll bring beer anyway.
Beer would be great! We'll have some veggie tofu kabobs so should be good unless you want something else! Have you been over before? Our address is ###############
Works for us! Thanks for your address!!
No problem! Looking forward to seeing you guys!
